<h1><span class="title_manage"><fmt:message key="update_study_details_continue" bundle="${resword}"/></span></h1>

<span class="title_Admin"><p><b><fmt:message key="section_c_conditions_and_eligibility" bundle="${resword}"/></b></p></span>
